    txpulses - transmit IR signal with pigpiod
    Johann Wiesner 2018
    dst0815@gmail.com

txpulses.h - c function for generating and playing waves with pigpiod

txpulses.pl - perl test script and emulation of remote control WH-TA01EE for inverter Toshiba Ras Suzumi


perl usage:
git clone https://github.com/dst0815/txpulses
cd txpulses
h2xs -n txpulses txpulses.h -lpigpiod_if2
mv txpulses.* txpulses
cd txpulses
perl Makefile.PL
make



